{
  "texts": [
    "No subscription was made to the ChatGPT Plus model which runs on GPT-4, a more advanced LLM that extends past the year 2021.",
    "Old OITE exam questions from the years 2020, 2021, 2022 were obtained and collaboratively screened by two primary authors (NJ, CG).",
    "Specific inclusion criteria included all questions with four multiple choice answers and text only.",
    "Due to ChatGPT's limitations, exclusion criteria included all questions with images, photography, or tables.",
    "Because ChatGPT uses memory retention to improve its performance, a new chatbox was created each time a question was input to reduce bias [5].Analysis of the data set was performed to initially look at how many questions ChatGPT-3.5 correctly answered."
  ]
}